Kenetswe Norah Mosenogi bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa si North West

Onye otu African National Congress, ọ bụ onye otu Executive Council (MEC) maka mmepe akụ na ụba, gburugburu ebe obibi, nchekwa na njem nleta na onye otu North West Provincial Legislature kemgbe Mee 2019
Mosenogi jere ozi dị ka osote odeakwụkwọ ukwu nke African National Congress Youth League site na 2011 ruo 2013.
Mosenogi nwetara nzere masta na nchịkwa azụmahịa na North-West University Business School. O nwekwara diplọma post-graduate na nlekota na nyocha site na Mahadum nke Witwatersrand

Mosenogi jere ozi dị ka onye nduzi nke ọrụ nkwado sayensị na onye na-ahụ maka mmekọrịta ndị omeiwu na Ngalaba Egwuregwu na Ntụrụndụ. Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dị ka onye enyemaka onye nchịkwa ụmụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum South Africa.
Mosenogi bụ onye isi otu African National Congress Youth League

A họpụtara ya na kọmitii na-ahụ maka mba na 2008. Ọ bụkwa onye kansụl na onye otu kọmitii onye isi obodo maka mmepe akụ na ụba nke Tlokwe Local Municipality, nke dị gburugburu Potchefstroom, ruo na ntuli aka ime obodo nke Mee 2011. N'ọnwa sochirinụ, a họpụtara Mosenogi ka ọ bụrụ osote odeakwụkwọ ukwu nke otu ndị ntorobịa ANC. Ọ nọchiri Steven Nogbeni ma jee ozi n'ọkwa ahụ ruo mgbe a gbasara usoro nduzi nke league maka oge ahụ na Machị 2013. Ọ bụ naanị nwanyị jere ozi na nduzi mba nke league maka oge ahụ. A họpụtara Thandi Moraka dị ka onye nọchiri ya na Septemba 2015.
Tupu ntuli aka na 8 Mee 2019, e debere Mosenogi na nke iri na abụọ na ndepụta mpaghara nke ANC nke ndị na-azọ ọkwa maka ndị omeiwu North West Provincial

Ụbọchị ole na ole ka e mesịrị, a họpụtara Mosenogi dị ka MEC maka mmepe akụ na ụba, gburugburu ebe obibi, nchekwa na njem nleta e guzobere ọhụrụ na kansụl ndị isi nke Job Mokgoro duziri. Ọ malitere ọrụ n'otu ụbọchị ahụ.
Àtụ:Members of the North West Provincial Legislature
